comment: He has been with Disney most of his life, he's never had any trouble as far as abusing women, and just because one person tried and almost succeeded to ruining his career, abusing him, you Disney should have stood by him not behind him. It's absolutely unprofessional, to assume, when he is Disney. Without him your money you are more for, and your image is now by far ruined. How could you not see the man who's been with you years, faithfully that this one person would be truthful.......wow! You cares more about your image more than the man who created above and beyond any of your imagination combined. Shame on all of you business reps, Corp heads who chose to fire him, late, drugs, alcohol or whatever, because you all worse and non of you can argue that, period...without him there will be no Disney as over the years do you not think we as the public notice the sick twisted sex and sadly the things that you put in your movies as cartoons?? Yes, we see them!! At least in his they are pure ..
